title: BREAKING: Supreme Court STRIKES DOWN Trump’s Tariffs – What Happens Now?
summary:
The Supreme Court struck down Trump’s tariff regime. What does this mean for the American economy? Does this mean tariffs are gone for good, or just for now? Are refunds on the way? 

Jessica Tarlov and Scott Galloway are here to talk through it. They talk about who the real winners and losers are, the politics of what comes next, and what American consumers can expect.
